---
title: Marry Me Chicken Rigatoni Includes recyclable aluminum tray
description: This pasta bake keeps cleanup to a minimum thanks to our oven-ready tray. Fresh rigatoni cooks up to a perfect al dente in the oven along with dark meat chicken and a velvety tomato cream sauce—with no prep required. Finish it with a swirl of tangy sun-dried tomato paste and sprinkle of nutty Parmesan for a convenient, delicious meal in a flash!
